Though you have travelled through many mines in the past, you see something that you have not seen before within the Iserngraf.

You see small piles of oddly-veined ore scattered on the floor. Perhaps Frithnoth would have some use for it.

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Iserngraf: Severance to be underway in order to access Iserngraf. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter Iserngraf in order to complete this quest.</rgb>

'This is interesting! We have overlooked this ore in the past, but if the Enemy was interested in it, perhaps we should be as well.'
Uncommon ore can be found in the Iserngraf.\n\nYou should collect uncommon ore and bring it to Frithnoth.
'This is interesting! We have overlooked this ore in the past but it seems as though the Enemy has an interest in it. Have you found any more of this? I would like to learn more of its properties.'
Bring the ore you collected to Frithnoth
